## 2. Admin Management
**Super admin only.** Regular admins get `403 Forbidden`.

### List All Admins
```
GET /api/v1/dallah/admins
```
Response `200`:
```json
{
  "admins": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "name": "K Saleh",
      "email": "ksaleh@aanaab.com",
      "role": "super_admin",
      "active": true,
      "created_at": "2026-03-08T11:55:58Z"
    }
  ]
}
```

### Register New Admin
```
POST /api/v1/dallah/admins
```
Request body:
```json
{
  "email": "newadmin@company.com",
  "password": "Secure@Pass1",
  "password_confirmation": "Secure@Pass1",
  "name": "Admin Name",
  "role": "admin"
}
```
Roles: `"admin"` or `"super_admin"`

Success `201`:
```json
{
  "admin": { "id": 2, "name": "Admin Name", "email": "newadmin@company.com", "role": "admin", "active": true, "created_at": "..." }
}
```

Error `422`:
```json
{ "error": "Validation failed", "details": ["Email has already been taken"] }
```

### Update Admin (role, name, activate/deactivate, password)
```
PATCH /api/v1/dallah/admins/:id
```
Request body (any subset):
```json
{
  "name": "New Name",
  "role": "super_admin",
  "active": false,
  "password": "NewPass@1",
  "password_confirmation": "NewPass@1"
}
```
Success `200`: returns updated admin object.

### Deactivate Admin
```
DELETE /api/v1/dallah/admins/:id
```
Success `200`: `{ "message": "Admin deactivated successfully" }`

Error `422` (cannot deactivate self): `{ "error": "Cannot deactivate your own account" }`

