## 3. Lookup Endpoints (Populate Dropdowns)

Call these when the dashboard loads to populate dropdowns. All work with JWT or static bearer.

### List Languages
```
GET /api/v1/dallah/languages
```
Response `200`:
```json
{
  "languages": [
    { "code": "1", "name": "arabic",  "locale": "ar" },
    { "code": "2", "name": "english", "locale": "en" },
    { "code": "3", "name": "ardu",    "locale": "ur" },
    { "code": "4", "name": "hendi",   "locale": "hi" }
  ]
}
```
Use `code` (the numeric string `"1"`, `"2"`, `"3"`, `"4"`) as the `lang` value in all user and enrollment requests.

### List Courses
```
GET /api/v1/dallah/courses
```
Response `200`:
```json
{
  "courses": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "course_name": "دليل تعليم القيادة النظري للمركبات  - مستوى متقدم (عربي)",
      "dallah_course_code": "P6h",
      "language": "arabic",
      "category": "private"
    }
  ]
}
```
Use `dallah_course_code` when submitting user creation and enrollment requests.
`category` maps to `licence_type`: `"private"` → `"private"`, `"motor"` → `"motor"`, `"public"` → `"public"`.

### List Branches
```
GET /api/v1/dallah/branches
```
Response `200`:
```json
{
  "branches": [
    {
      "id": 22,
