## 5. Enrollment Endpoints

All enrollment endpoints require `national_id` (exact 10-digit) to identify the user.

### Create Enrollment (add user to a course)
```
POST /api/v1/dallah/enrollments
```
```json
{
  "national_id": "1234567890",
  "courses": [
    { "dallah_course_code": "P6h", "lang": "1", "licence_type": "private" }
  ]
}
```

### Delete Enrollment
```
DELETE /api/v1/dallah/enrollments
```
```json
{
  "national_id": "1234567890",
  "courses": [
    { "dallah_course_code": "P6h", "lang": "1", "licence_type": "private" }
  ]
}
```

### Replace Enrollment (delete old + create new in one call)
```
POST /api/v1/dallah/enrollments/replace
```
```json
{
  "national_id": "1234567890",
  "courses": [
    {
      "old": { "dallah_course_code": "P6h", "lang": "1", "licence_type": "private" },
      "new": { "dallah_course_code": "M15h", "lang": "2", "licence_type": "motor" }
    }
  ]
}
```

### Get Progress Report for a User
```
POST /api/v1/dallah/enrollments/progress_report
```
```json
{
  "national_id": "1234567890",
  "dallah_course_code": "P6h",
  "lang": "1",
  "licence_type": "private"
}
```

