## 7. Common Error Responses

| Status | Meaning | Body |
|---|---|---|
| 401 | Missing/invalid/expired token | `{ "error": "authorization required", "status": 401 }` |
| 403 | Logged in but not super_admin | `{ "error": "Forbidden", "status": 403 }` |
| 404 | Admin/user not found | `{ "error": "Admin not found" }` |
| 422 | Validation error | `{ "error": "Validation failed", "details": ["..."] }` |
| 503 | LMS/Keycloak unavailable | `{ "error": "Service unavailable", "message": "..." }` |

