## 8. Suggested Frontend Flow

```
App Load
  └── GET /auth/me
        ├── 200 → restore session, check role
        └── 401 → redirect to Login page

Login Page
  └── POST /auth/login
        ├── 200 → save token, redirect to Dashboard
        └── 401 → show "Invalid credentials"

Dashboard Load
  ├── GET /languages (populate language dropdown)
  ├── GET /courses   (populate course dropdown)
  └── GET /branches  (populate branch dropdown)

Bulk Upload
  ├── GET /users/bulk_csv/template  (download CSV template)
  └── POST /users/bulk_csv          (upload filled CSV, show summary + errors)

Add User Form
  └── POST /users
        ├── 201 → success toast
        └── 422 → show field errors inline

User Search
  └── GET /users?q=<input>  (debounce 300ms)

Enrollment Actions
  ├── POST /enrollments/replace  (change course)
  └── DELETE /enrollments        (remove from course)

Attendance / Progress View
  └── GET /notifications
        └── display table with user + started date
```

