## 9. Super Admin vs Admin Permissions

| Action | admin | super_admin |
|---|---|---|
| Login, view profile | ✅ | ✅ |
| All user/enrollment/notification endpoints | ✅ | ✅ |
| `GET/POST/PATCH/DELETE /admins` | ❌ 403 | ✅ |

Check `admin.role === "super_admin"` from the login response to conditionally show the "Manage Admins" section.

